title: BEAUTIFUL STUDIO || TONS OF NATURAL LIGHT
posting_body: ['Heat and Hot Water Included!!', 'Welcome to 832 Quincy Street, a beautiful brownstone tucked away on a quiet street in Brooklyn.', 'This spacious and sun-drenched studio space is a great option for a couple or person looking for an upgrade while also staying within budget!', 'This loft-like floorplan has oversized windows that allow natural light to pour in, exposed brick architecture, and a nice divider that offers separation to the studio apartment between the living space/kitchen and bedroom.', 'Maple cabinetry, granite countertops, and a fully tiled bathroom compliment the apartment’s rustic design.', 'J/M/Z trains at Gates Avenue and A/C trains at Utica are a short walk from the apartment.', 'There are a plethora of bar and restaurant options within walking distance of the apartment.', 'Grocery stores and a gym around the corner.', 'Lease Term: 12 months', 'Must meet income and credit requirements.', 'Guarantors welcome.', 'To view the unit text, call or email anytime!']
